snippet.title: Fractured Core Trailer
snippet.description:
Free DEMO on steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1238990/Fractured_Core/

Fractured Core is a cyberpunk JRPG set in 2105 Germany. Follow Michael, a Raven Operator of Athena, as he start his journey to uncover the truth that was hidden throughout history.

#cyberpunk #pixelart #godot #indiegame #jrpg
